title: [Vornavis, Peasant Holdings]
description: The sharp buzz of crickets rises from a field.  Left untilled this season, clover has moved in and the field is a bed of deep green sprinkled with dots of dark lavender.

Sunlight flashes from the wings of bees buzzing between the clover blossoms.  Left untilled this season, clover has moved in and the field is a bed of deep green sprinkled with dots of bright lavender.
paths: Obvious paths: north, northeast, east, southeast, south, northwest
